{"tid":941950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幣少爺洗定屎忽】撒錢若帶有目的 　法律界：可能干犯公安條例","createTime":"2018-12-15T08:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T15:39:35.000Z","uid":202698,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a426758119f64bb4f4b2fc96fe20f5f443c66d87","tid":941950,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181215/large/1544860856_96e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181215%2Flarge%2F1544860856_96e9.jpg&h=04f70ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深水埗有人由天台撒下大批銀紙，引起市民瘋搶。<span style=\"color: red;\">法律界人士稱，如果掉錢者有目的、有動機地做出撒錢的行為，有可能會干犯《公安條例》，最高可被判監禁及罰款。不過，由於鈔票被視為遺棄的財物，撿拾者未必就有罪。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黃國桐律師稱，要是能證實撒鈔票的人有動機、有目的，是一個「well planning(有計劃)」的行為，而此行為預期是會引人注目、引起混亂，則有可能干犯《公安條例》-在公眾地方喧嘩、或作出擾亂秩序的行為，意圖激起他人破壞社會安寧，或可能會導致破壞社會安寧。有關條例，最高可被判罰監禁12個月及罰款5千元。黃說：「等於搵個場做SHOW，佢須要負責。」</span><br />\n<br />\n至於是因為搶錢而發生的意外，卻難以歸咎於撒錢者而作出追究。黃國桐解釋，因為這並非必然的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：執錢無罪，派錢有罪<br />\n<br />\n幣少爺宣傳有關活動而派錢片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Epoch.Cryptocurrency/videos/2040850349291318/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FEpoch.Cryptocurrency%2Fvideos%2F2040850349291318%2F&d=CZC%2BDMS16IBZWuicu0fkRm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7e805f0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Epoch.Cryptocurrency/videos/2040850349291318/</a>"},{"pid":"fe46a709b28b52d848ed4591f023e7d0ef9ac97a","tid":941950,"uid":202698,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/finance/w273h185/20180305/GTvV-fxipenm9157501.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ffinance%2Fw273h185%2F20180305%2FGTvV-fxipenm9157501.jpg&h=6d0c62b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqwhM0K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqwhM0K.png&h=1bcf1493&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31f92a0d4b57e010f9f8186fd247eeba8cf577f4","tid":941950,"uid":202698,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"今次仲要玩鳩埋班差佬，隨時加多條浪費警力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5180ccc3bbc802d67315343c7cd8ab4d03d18116","tid":941950,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc9d6b59f837ebcb2e9471d89c9d8ccc483582d0","tid":941950,"uid":29880,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:01:07.000Z","msg":"政府唔起訴佢<br />\n以後去政總撒錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e511f56a738c1421c1c4c49187c561833c071a72","tid":941950,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:01:23.000Z","msg":"目的係想人開心咁點計先"},{"pid":"32eeb1f0cddcef18f2c8f0fd6ec706e381467f92","tid":941950,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:02:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cd2c264c1d31b4a1f236f043072dddd4b5b9718","tid":941950,"uid":15140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32eeb1f0cddcef18f2c8f0fd6ec706e381467f92","tid":941950,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"5180ccc3bbc802d67315343c7cd8ab4d03d18116","tid":941950,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:02:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cc9537ad747503c293aefc6d48d73b530c09d3","tid":941950,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:07:56.000Z","msg":"大撒幣"},{"pid":"b980ed5ff626be53f906cb793ab2b7a83d5620d2","tid":941950,"uid":60341,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e511f56a738c1421c1c4c49187c561833c071a72","tid":941950,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:01:23.000Z","msg":"目的係想人開心咁點計先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"佢好明顯宣傳緊個垃圾買幣平台喎"},{"pid":"5c79126a7b3a50f4a51501967ff7aa5489eaecac","tid":941950,"uid":13084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"佢冇親手掉喎"},{"pid":"b6c0c42078c302df48fe8d7e17480b931092e8dd","tid":941950,"uid":202698,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:13:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img1.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20140313152112/evchk/images/1/10/Wholefamdiethistime.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20140313152112%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F10%2FWholefamdiethistime.png&h=0ee4b5e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幣少爺，洗定屎忽啦，隨時加多項浪費警力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1636ae0efae4476a11335490d2f07a2ef49f1176","tid":941950,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:17:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5d73e2770da165186d63b0e2383d1fb2c0a2df9","tid":941950,"uid":25560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:43:00.000Z","msg":"拉佢坐監，充公佢身家就啱"},{"pid":"ceb26576d8b39b403e405641a82ff8fc7cb11bcc","tid":941950,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0138435a343a896d78023dabd1fc0e305a2ec682","tid":941950,"uid":202698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T13:53:05.000Z","msg":"深水埗今日(15日)有人將大疊100港元鈔票從天台撒下，途人瘋狂執錢。民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸認為，因有關行為引起市民瘋狂爭搶，雖無人受傷，但已產生混亂，她要求警方跟進及調查有關金錢是否合法所得，而市民使用有關金錢是否違法，警方有需要交代。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">本身為律師的立法會議員何君堯認為，有關行徑或涉及高空擲物，事實上亦引起市面混亂，屬於破壞社會安寧，直言警方一定要跟進，或邀請相關人士協助調查，避免再有同類事件發生。</span><br />\n<br />\n立法會保安事務委員會主席陳克勤表示，社會上有心派錢的人不多，但不能排除日後會出現模仿行為，屆時又會引起社會混亂，<span style=\"color: red;\">對治安及市民財產構成危險，而今次疑有人有預謀地拍片，於網絡上已留下可跟進的軌迹，故警方有需要跟進，防止有人「有樣學樣」。</span>他續指，前線警員面對的挑戰大，隨時由一件小事引起其他人圍觀及拍照，繼而引起混亂，故警方需要加強前線警員的訓練以應付類似情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3098027c32ebd3b0db44cf95efe9c71026c0d9b5","tid":941950,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e511f56a738c1421c1c4c49187c561833c071a72","tid":941950,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T09:01:23.000Z","msg":"目的係想人開心咁點計先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"引起混亂一樣犯法<br />\n唔理目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇個官點判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}